text: Dommartin is a former commune. It is found in the Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes region in the Ain department in the east of France. On 1 January 2018, it was merged into the new commune of Bâgé-Dommartin.Arrêté préfectoral 8 December 2017 == References == Category:Former communes in Ain
title: Dommartin, Ain
